@startuml abel-gr_warehouse-robot

[Unity Environment] as Unity
[CoppeliaSim Simulation] as CoppeliaSim
[Web Interface] as WebUI
[Speech-to-Text Cloud Function] as STT
[OCR Module] as OCR
[Robot Control Module] as RobotControl
[Path Planning Module] as PathPlanning

Unity --> CoppeliaSim : Remote API
WebUI --> Unity : User Interaction
WebUI --> STT : Speech Input
STT --> WebUI : Text Output
CoppeliaSim --> OCR : Image Data
OCR --> RobotControl : Label Information
RobotControl --> CoppeliaSim : Robot Commands
PathPlanning --> RobotControl : Navigation Instructions

@enduml